description.en: Pirates find treasure in exchange for more powerful INF treasure chests; Our mission is to build a comprehensive platform of digital character pirates that will allow millions of players to enter the world of NFT and blockchain-based gaming in a simple, innovative and fun way. Here, you can become rich and powerful. The sea is always the homeland and the place to make money for strongest pirates, build an army for yourself and earn a lot for yourself. Going to sea is dangerous and challenging, but it enriches us.
